<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-338] Simplify maven structure</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-338</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As per some email to the dev list, I plan to streamline and simplify the maven structure, by eliminating the &apos;maven&apos; directory and letting the top-level POM be the parent, moving release packaging to a separate distribution directory.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I do not plan to post patches here.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
